title: Counter-Strike 1.6 CSL Edition 2017
description:
Counter-Strike 1.6 CSL , League is waiting for you ! 
Now you can play in another experience and with a highly FPS ! 
The gameplay wasn't modified , all is based on the clasic CS 1.6 ! 
There was much optimized things which will help you to play at the better experience ! 
This client game kit is now as an installer , more faster than archive ! 

Few things which was added on this version : 

# A guard which will verify all servers activity [ If one is trying to modify your game client , the guard will block it ] 
# A list of servers updated weekly ! 
# Now all your configurations will be saved 
# New skins for a HIGH FPS and on the worst PC 
# The client kit works on all multiplayer server [ which have the protocol 47/48 ] 
# Includes the latest bots 
# The archive max. size is 222 [ more less then other clients ] 

NOTE : To run the game , you can use one of the launchers which i offered to you : 
- Counter-Strike 1.6.exe [ The principal executable ] 
- Counter-Strike 1.6.vbs [ Another executable file based on Virtual Basic programming language ] 
- Counter-Strike 1.6.bat [ Another executable file based on Batch programming language ]
